title: Myths Vegetarian Product Speciality Store
description: A small vegetarian store selling a variety of products including both frozen and shelf packaged mock meats labeled as vegetarian. Also carries vegan items; please ask or read labels. Located next door to Legend Vegetarian Cafe (not affiliated).
streetAddress: S/L 11, Lot 745, Jalan Datuk Tawi Sli, 3rd Exchange Commercial Centre
